query_next_donation_from: select top (1) PerC.UniqueId, convert(varchar, ApD.NextDonationDate, 104) Ent from PersonCards PerC join AppointedDonationTypes ApD on PerC.UniqueId = ApD.DonorId where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and ApD.NextDonationDate < getdate() and ApD.NextDonationDate > dateadd(year, -10, getdate())
